Name: Operation S
About the game: A 2D single-player strategy game about a rescue mission that takes place in space, and it is up to the rescue team to venture out and find the missing astronauts, to rescue them from the dangers of space. The player must rotate the rings and align the astronauts on top, for them to enter the ship safely, and escape.
